description: Behold, I come as a thief. Blessed is he that watcheth, and keepeth his garments, lest he walk naked, and they see his shame Christ declares.  Have you ever considered the context of this scripture?  The word behold indicates to us that this scripture and its context is worthy of our deep contemplation so that we are not classed as those who walk naked.  The previous two verses bring to view a false, apostate three-fold union that will be active and evident at this time.  As the biblical methods of study are employed, it is unmistakable who/what constitutes the dragon, the beast, and the false prophet from whom are emanating the spirits of devils working miracles.  The dragon represents paganism and the civil leaders of various nations; the beast is the Papacy; and the false prophet symbolizes professed protestant ministers especially in the United States.  Again coming from the mouths of these three entities is seen unclean spirits like frogs working miracles.  The symbolism of frogs with its association with miracles should bring ones mind back to the plague of frogs in ancient Egypt, which was counterfeited by the magicians just prior to the great exodus.  Satan counterfeited this miracle/plague so that the people would remain in the house of bondage which is nothing other than heathenism, sin, and false worship.  Today, the unclean spirits like frogs which are styled as the spirits of devils working miracles, represent false worship, but more specifically Sunday worship.  It is clear, to those students of prophecy who have been watching the signs of the times as they are revealed in current events that all three entitiesthe dragon, the beast, and the false prophethave been persistently, aggressively, and persuasively calling for the observance of Sunday as a day of rest, and urging such to be legislated. This three-fold, apostate union is being cemented as leaders of each aforementioned entity are meeting and have recently met, vowing to fulfill Jesus prayer for unity in John 17, and hoping that such a unity will be realized in their day, this day. The objective of this union is to direct worship that belongs only to the Creator God  to the Beast Powerthe Papacy. As this push for unity and compulsory Sunday observance is being agitated, we are instructed by Christ to Behold for his coming is imminent and that we should therefore be clad with his garments so that the shame of our nakedness does not appear.  The sad reality is however, that lukewarm Laodiceans (people professing to be a part of Gods remnant church) are naked-- some because of willful disobedience, others from the subtle mixture of truth and error, and still a greater number because of the leadership.  The counsel to us at this time is to buy of Christ that white raiment which He so graciously is offering us.  It is in the mount with God, the secret place of communion, studying and earnestly pleading with God, where this garment can only be obtained.  As this experience leads us to victory over sin, the promise is ours for the claiming: He that overcometh, the same shall be clothed in white raiment; and I will not blot [spew] out his name out of the book of life, but I will confess his name before my Father, and before his angels.  Be blessed as you watch, listen, study, and apply the principles contained in this sermon.
fulltitle: Dragon, Beast, & False Prophet Unite! Laodiceans Still Naked
